		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The goal of this research is the synergistic integration of multi-modality three-dimensional microscopic imaging techniques.  A microscope employing multi-wavelength optical and confocal microscopes and acoustic 3D microscopes will be developed and integrated into a computer controlled, mechanically scanned system for studying thick histological tissue specimens.  Registration of similar and disparated modalities will be studied.  Synergistic combination will be through development of new multi-modality fusion algorithms and multi-resolution segmentation techniques.  Integration of these techniques into a demonstration test-bed will allow for pathologists and medical imaging researchers to explore aspects of synergistic imaging interactively on real tissue samples.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
